posting_body: ['Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Url: <URL>', 'Our community boasts amenities including a BBQ and picnic area, an outdoor swimming pool, and a fitness center.', 'Community Amenities', 'Online Resident Portal • On-Site Management •', 'On-Site Maintenance • BBQ/Picnic Area • Courtyard • Fitness Center • High Speed Internet • Laundry Facilities • Pool • Available 24/7 to Assist You • Controlled Access/Gated • Near Public Transportation', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Cable Ready • Stainless Steel Appliances • Quartz or Granite Counter-tops • Built-in Shelving • Townhomes Available', '•', 'Dishwasher •', 'Disposal • Efficient Appliances • Hardwood Inspired Floors • Refrigerator • Gas Range • Air Conditioner • Fireplace* • Vaulted Ceilings • Private Balcony/Patio', 'Contact us today to tour our thoughtfully designed apartment homes.', 'The Woods at Toluca Lake is a unique community outfitted with a plethora of amenities including vaulted ceilings, Berber carpet, wide plank flooring, an interior gas fireplace, in addition to a central heat and air conditioning system.', 'Burbank is known for maintaining a resident-friendly, small town atmosphere, which combined with a strong business climate, has made Burbank a fixture on Los Angeles Magazine’s “10 Best Cities to Live in Southern California.”', 'The Woods at Toluca Lake', '316 North Maple Street', 'Burbank, CA 91505', 'Federal law prohibits housing discrimination on the basis of race, color, national origin, religion, sex, familial status, or disability.', '* Prices and availability are subject to change without notice.', 'Mon-Fri:', '9AM-6PM', 'Saturday-Sunday: Closed']
